These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, cain, oliveros
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Cigar   | oliveros | cain | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Beverage   | coffee | hot-chocolate | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, poker, whist
1. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
2. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Game   | monopoly | poker | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, rat
1. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Pet   | ferret | rat | frog |

 #################################

 
